    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A re-awakening of an old flash point and click adventure game that will bring you back to your childhood (well for most of you). You play as a peaceful zombie who is on an adventure, as you play the game the story enfolds. Try to find out who you are and what's going on and maybe what the future holds. It is based in an post apocalyptic land out in the desert where you parked up your RV and set up base for a while. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this short but sweet little point and click adventure game, you will come across characters who need your help, or at least will help you in your quest. You will also get to read up on what and why things have happened to get you to this point.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Did you know, in the future they produce brains in cans? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game has been updated for the steam release, including some new graphics, scenes, clickable items, and some quality of life updates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We do hope you will support us and enjoy the adventure so we are able to continue on with the sequel(s)!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013860/extras/a08388b4fa1847964a66cdc861a061f3.avif?t=1734602553\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3013860/extras_big/a08388b4fa1847964a66cdc861a061f3.avif?t=1734602553 width=800 height=650 /></span></p>",
